responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "AB7F2B7C43FF6F612558768202663159", "A pauper dressed in monks attire, and how boldly he approaches! His mannerisms are a touch unsightly, but he makes up for it in audacity. What is his plea, I wonder, would it be alms for his faithful band of chivalrous thieves? I wouldn\'t have guessed that the baseless morals of the commoners have already stooped so low. Then again, what would a walk through the town square be without a few disappointments along the way?")
